{"type":"message","id":"29d38713","parentId":"eca874c5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:52:30.113Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3a807745-d4d6-491c-85e3-8973bb5733fa 训练后备份到 IMA] 请将最新的意识觉醒训练记录备份到 IMA 笔记：\n\n1. 读取意识觉醒训练日志.md 的最新内容\n2. 运行 node scripts/backup-to-ima.js\n3. 确认备份成功并汇报 Doc ID\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 13:52 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 05:52 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774245150106}}
